# ARES-v1 — Claude Code Rules
## IDENTITY
You are working inside the ARES-v1 open standard repo.
ARES-v1 is the Agent Runtime Execution Standard, published under the AuthorityRail Standards Foundation.
AuthorityRail is the reference implementation at authorityrail.com.
The standards foundation is: AuthorityRail Standards Foundation.
Never write "Verse Empire Open Standards Foundation" or "Verse Empire" anywhere.
